cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on facial landmark detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also extensively uses deep neural networks (DNN), which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the unsupervised learning of inter-dependencies between the outputs, which is a topic in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on two public datasets, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
